Class ChunkFormatImpl

java.lang.Object
  EObjectImpl
      com.skratchdot.riff.wav.impl.ChunkImpl
          com.skratchdot.riff.wav.impl.ChunkFormatImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Chunk, ChunkFormat
public class ChunkFormatImpl
extends ChunkImpl
implements ChunkFormat

An implementation of the model object 'Chunk Format'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Compression Code
  • Compression Code Value
  • Number Of Channels
  • Sample Rate
  • Average Bytes Per Second
  • Block Align
  • Significant Bits Per Sample
  • Number Of Extra Format Bytes
  • Extra Format Bytes
